# Agent onboarding

At the start of every chat, **read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root** before scanning individual files.

That file has:
- Production and local URLs
- Health-check commands
- Logs (Railway, Vercel, local)
- Live session APIs and admin snapshot scripts
- Repo structure and common troubleshooting

Use `docs/findings-ai/` only when you need deeper product or architecture detail.
